ard-title\">Capacity Rightsizing Intelligence</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">**Rightsizing and forecasting layer** for virtual infrastructure, turning telemetry into actionable capacity and utilization decisions.</p></div></article><article class=\"card border border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"card-title\">Compute Baseline Optimization</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">Performance baseline tuning for compute-heavy virtualization clusters.</p></div></article><article class=\"card border border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"card-title\">Cross-Tier Storage Orchestration</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">Policy-driven orchestration across performance, capacity, and archive tiers.</p></div></article><article class=\"card border border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"card-title\">Elastic Compute Placement</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">Adaptive placement and balancing strategy for compute-heavy virtual workloads.</p></div></article><article class=\"card border border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"card-title\">Fabric Segmentation Enforcement</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">Network segmentation enforcement patterns for tenant and workload isolation.</p></div></article><article class=\"card border border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"card-title\">Hybrid Disaster Recovery for VMS</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">**Cross-site resilience blueprint** for Vates VMS workloads, covering replication, failover, and recovery validation.</p></div></article><article class=\"card border border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"card-title\">Observability and Cost Governance</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">**Unified visibility plus cost-aware governance** for virtualized estates, combining operational KPIs with financial accountability.</p></div></article><article class=\"card border border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"card-title\">Secure Multi-Tenant Hosting Blueprint</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">**Security-first architecture** to isolate tenants and enforce policy governance across shared virtualization infrastructure.</p></div></article><article class=\"card border border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"card-title\">Tiering and Archive Automation</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">Storage lifecycle automation for tiering, archival, and retention control.</p></div></article><article class=\"card border border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"card-body\"><h2 class=\"card-title\">VMS Modernization Factory</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-base-content/80\">**Structured migration path** to modernize operations while moving workloads to Vates VMS, with staged cutovers and repeatable landing zones.</p></div></article><!--]--></section></section></main><footer class=\"footer border-t border-base-300 bg-base-100\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex min-h-16 w-[min(1080px,92vw)] items-center text-base-content/70\"><p>Vates Alliance Network (VAN)</p></div></footer></div></div><div id=\"teleports\"></div><script type=\"application/json\" data-nuxt-logs=\"nuxt-app\">[[1],{\"date\":2,\"args\":3,\"type\":6,\"level\":7,\"tag\":8,\"filename\":9,\"stack\":10},[\"Date\",\"2026-02-21T15:22:56.624Z\"],[4,5],\"Vite server hmr 1 files\",\"in 1.188ms\",\"success\",3,\"\",\"file://node_modules/@nuxt/vite-builder/dist/vite-node-entry.mjs\",[11,16,21],{\"function\":12,\"source\":13,\"line\":14,\"column\":15},\"vite_node_entry_default\",\"/Users/jb/code/VAN-frontend/node_modules/@nuxt/vite-builder/dist/vite-node-entry.mjs\",17,11,{\"function\":17,\"source\":18,\"line\":19,\"column\":20},\"process.processTicksAndRejections\",\"node:internal/process/task_queues\",105,5,{\"function\":22,\"source\":23,\"line\":24,\"column\":25},\"async O